author: Julie Mack | jmack1@mlive.com
title: See percentage of births paid by Medicaid in your Michigan county

organizations.name: michigan department of health and human services

text: Medicaid paid for 43.5 percent of Michigan births in 2015, and the proportion was 60 percent or over in 16 Michigan counties, according to data from the Michigan Department of Health and Human Services.
